    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Performance is enhanced by Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers and a set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical systems are dialed for high-revving throttle response and precise lateral dynamics. A true enthusiast\u2019s driver, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
