      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of respectful use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather bolsters show only light creasing, and all original floor mats are included. Every feature, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have kept a meticulous log of all maintenance, including a recent synthetic oil change and a brake pad replacement performed last season. This car delivers a firm, quiet ride and is ready for immediate delivery without the need for any upcoming major service.",
      "price": 34850.0,
